                            jump to other results
                        </a></div></div><ol class="sense_single" htag="ol"><li class="sense" id="advertisingstandardsauthority_sng_1" hclass="sense" htag="li"><span class="sensetop" hclass="sensetop" htag="span"><span class="def" htag="span" hclass="def">an independent organization, founded in 1962, which checks that advertisements do not lie or make false claims about a product. Anyone can ask the <span class="dh">Advertising Standards Authority</span> to investigate an advertisement. If there is a problem with it, the Authority may then tell the company to change or remove it.</span></span>    <div id="ring-links-box">
